modName: s6o6t LORE - Dark Anchors ruins and Dolmens
summary: This lore mod adds 6 Dolmens and Dark Anchors ruins to Eastmarch and to Rift to the places they were in ESO.
descriptionHtml:
While playing Elder Scrolls Online, I thought why not bring some structures like Dolmens to Skyrim? And then I did a Dark Anchor model but bringing it to the Skyrim world isn't actually lore because of Dragonfires, you know. But adding six Dolmens from ESO to Eastmarch and to Rift seemed to me like a pretty lore idea.
This is my second mod for Skyrim.Â This mod adds 6 Dolmens and Dark Anchors ruins to Eastmarch and to Rift to the places they were in ESO.

(btw, sorry if my English is bad, it's not my native language :D)
